{"tid":736434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加國男陳屍家中多日　愛狗因太餓吃掉半個屍體","createTime":"2018-07-10T08:49:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T09:56:55.000Z","uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"67ef0d7f021af70822a707cfe30d951355e2e5ed","tid":736434,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T08:49:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180710/_2018071013312121168.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180710%2F_2018071013312121168.jpg&h=65c347d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名在泰國獨自生活的加拿大男子死在自己的公寓內，令人驚駭的是，他的屍體被發現時已經被自己養的寵物犬吃掉了一半。<br />\n<br />\n62歲的加拿大男子派丁森（Glenn Pattinson）獨自居住在泰國已經3年，和他一起生活的還有一條名叫Cujo的5歲愛犬。近日，鄰居們發現派丁森已經很長時間沒有像往常一樣出門遛狗了，而Cujo卻一直在房間裏不停地吠，這讓鄰居們察覺到了不對勁，於是他們報警。<br />\n<br />\n上周五（6日），警員到場時發現現場慘不忍睹。派丁森赤身裸體地躺在臥室地板上，已經去世多日。他的屍體頭顱現骨，胸口一片血肉模糊，肋骨也裸露在外。而Cujo就坐在主人身邊，滿嘴都是乾涸的血跡。在主人去世期間，這隻寵物犬由於過度飢餓而不得不將主人屍體作為糧食，吃掉近半個屍體。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，派丁森是糖尿病患者，最近去醫院接受了治療，但很快便出院回家。警方表示，他們並未在此次死亡事件中發現謀殺的跡象。派丁森被發現時沒有穿任何衣物，死亡時間大約在被發現的7到10天前。當地警方表示：「這隻寵物犬就在他身邊，連續幾天滴水未進，屋內也沒有打鬥和翻查痕跡。」、「我們知道死者是一個人居住的。現在這具屍體已經交由法醫部門處理，以找出確切的死因。」、「我們也將會聯繫大使館，通知家屬為其籌辦後事。」<br />\n<br />\n34歲的貝爾是派丁森的鄰居，他稱派丁森是一個友善的外國人。貝爾說，派丁森非常喜歡他的狗，每天晚上都會帶牠去散步，也經常會結交不同的女性朋友。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180710/_2018071013312187766.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180710%2F_2018071013312187766.jpg&h=7fd5078e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n62歲的加拿大男子派丁森（Glenn Pattinson）在3年前搬到泰國居住。（網圖）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/761953\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F761953&d=yJ2kETKxjOjjyTvR2w%2FLZNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=ff98aad0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F761953&h=899cf21d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/761953</a>"},{"pid":"5b200b180c60ce6f545b0334ac93b0e1d56e371b","tid":736434,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T08:50:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3ec6550232d75ee886c567c38fb6c9f4d291fed","tid":736434,"uid":111253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T08:51:49.000Z","msg":"死左先食, 算係咁啦"},{"pid":"035e4fea4301fe35295e5dc0f890b222d70ad578","tid":736434,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T08:52:47.000Z","msg":"養狼狗咬膥袋"},{"pid":"608c70de094673d3c0eef4b75af444d16def3a3d","tid":736434,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T08:54:16.000Z","msg":"等睇道德撚審判隻狗. <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f11838bb4ab2735f6fb826ecf10525cd8d74c83a","tid":736434,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T08:54:22.000Z","msg":"狗撚成日話貓先會食屍"},{"pid":"2e1042a7387877d0a5be60009dcd52e42f576b75","tid":736434,"uid":2140,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T08:54:26.000Z","msg":"幾識嘆<br />\n加拿大搵錢拎去泰國玩<br />\n實晚晚屌幾個賓妹+人妖"},{"pid":"358a9f5f5663d69a939efaa6bc6e97005f6255e2","tid":736434,"uid":183383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T08:54:34.000Z","msg":"家明??"},{"pid":"e5340da78480b618a5114563cd12c213f0194ed2","tid":736434,"uid":29314,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T09:10:57.000Z","msg":"如果係我，我會無所謂。<br />\n<br />\n我愛我隻狗，我願意付出我既身體等佢唔使餓死。"},{"pid":"c8909782423aa2c3d88901322a71cbc793e98673","tid":736434,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"358a9f5f5663d6